result.execSummary:
The defendant Justin A Brown was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Justin A Brown is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Justin A Brown was found guilty of Vehicle Operator Flee/Elude Officer, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 346.04(3).
